### Create a new breed
POST http://localhost:5000/api/breeds
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Golden Retriever"
}

### Get all breeds
GET http://localhost:5000/api/breeds

### Get a specific breed by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/breeds/1

### Update a breed
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/breeds/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Labrador Retriever"
}

### Delete a breed
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/breeds/1